Title: Warbands: Warbanding Together
Description:
Hey $n, some friends and I have teamed up to form a Warband and are working on something that should make cooperation so much easier, even when we're apart!

We just need a little help with this last step.

Come find us in Gadgetzan when you get a moment!
ObjectivesText: Meet Blue and her Warband in Gadgetzan.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Blue and her Warband in Gadgetzan
